            <scopecontent id="aspace_53248396e3fa53a80e0a185d9d9fee3a">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series I. Writings contains extensive material relating to an unpublished novel by Brush with the initial working title "Story of Sylvia," changed later to "Lover Come Back." The novel, started in the early 1940s, went through multiple revisions, and includes corrections and comments from editors. Materials relating to the work include research files, outlines and synopses, drafts, and supplementary material, such as excerpts, discards, and schedules.</p>
            </scopecontent>
